The paper discusses machine learning methods and data analytics tasks based on similarity triplets. This falls under the broad category of machine learning and artificial intelligence, which is covered by cs.LG and cs.AI. The paper also mentions applications in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL), which are common areas of research in machine learning. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of crowd-sourcing for obtaining triplet data, which may involve privacy and security concerns, falling under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR).
